Class PhysicalEntity

java.lang.Object
semsim.SemSimObject

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
CompositePhysicalEntity, CustomPhysicalEntity, ReferencePhysicalEntity
public abstract class PhysicalEntity
extends PhysicalModelComponent
Class for working with the physical entities represented in a model. Analogous to 'OPB:Physics continuant': Physics continuants are portions of primitive physics entites that may be spatially-bounded (e.g, a heart, a portion of blood, a cell's cytoplasmic sodium ions) or may be spatially-unbounded (e.g., an electrical field or gravitational potential field).
